Hey James,

A new lead has been registered inside the Google Sheets: {{1.message.toolCalls[].function.arguments.Name}}, with a budget of {{1.message.toolCalls[].function.arguments.Budget}} and wants the property to be in {{1.message.toolCalls[].function.arguments.Location}}

messages.content:
#Context 
We have just asked the user which day they would like to schedule a viewing. You will be given the current date and their response.

#Instructions 
You must return the start and end time in JSON format. This is essential for our company.

#Example Output

{"startTime": "2024-06-28T08:00:00.00", "endTime": "2024-06-28T18:00:00.00"}

#Rules
-The start time must always be at 09:00 (08 AM)
-The end time must always be at 18:00 (6 PM)
-The start and end times must always be on the same day
-The returned day must always be after the current day

Current time: {{now}}

The day that the user has requested: {{1.message.toolCalls[].function.arguments.BookDay}}

messages.content:
Determine if the Real Estate Agent is filled up and has no free time the day that the user has chosen. 

Here you have the busy slots (each slot is of 1 hour): {{11.calendars.`tribexagency@gmail.com`.busy}}

If the number of busy slots equals to 9 then output Busy, if it doesn't, just output Free

#Example output
Free

messages.content:
#Context 
We have just asked the user when they would like to schedule a viewing. You will be given the current date and their response.

#Instructions 
You must return the start and end time in JSON format. This is essential for our company.

#Example Output

{"startTime": "2024-06-28T08:00:00.00", "endTime": "2024-06-28T18:00:00.00","chosenTime": "2024-06-28T10:00:00.00"}

#Rules
-The start time must always be at 09:00 (08 AM)
-The end time must always be at 18:00 (6 PM)
-The start and end times must always be on the same day
-The returned time must always be after the current time
-Use the same format as the example but adapted for the requested time

Current time: {{now}}

The day and time requested by the user: {{27.`5`}}{{1.message.toolCalls[].function.arguments.HourViewing}}
